{
  "stem": "7455.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Germans, we went on across-- across the road, stay for safety.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they occupied those quarters, the private houses and our house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were from the-- watching from the window the tro-- the Allied troops marching in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were admiring their spunk, the way they're full of life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Their soldiers were walking with sores, with torn shoes, torn up, not shaved, because they were on the retreat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To me, that was music.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one woman says, oh, God knows what our Fuehrer's doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He meant well for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it didn't turn out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Even though the Americans were coming in, even though it-- they could be retreat and it's dangerous, I could not resist anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When she cried, the Fuehrer meant well, I cried out, if Fuehrer wanted to rob and kill the whole world and feed their own Germans at the expense of people-- I said, I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My parents, my family were killed, because he wanted [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], this dentist, she was hysterical afraid that I'm going to point her out to the American.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Americans are not going to kill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They are liberators.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They are not going to do what you did to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then that night the soldiers were moving in from the windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were seeing them coming in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, perhaps I spoke too soon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Should they retreat?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I should have held my mouth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when she was sorry for Hitler-- oh, God knows what our Fuerher's doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I couldn't hold it back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as time went on, the troops were-- the more I saw them coming, the more I felt that it's not a temporary occupation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
